GET http://localhost:8087/coupons/1

### Validate Coupon Code
POST http://localhost:8087/coupons/validate?code=WELCOME10&userId=1

### Validate Invalid Coupon
POST http://localhost:8087/coupons/validate?code=INVALID&userId=1

